lgp.core.environment.dataset

Interface DatasetLoader<TData>

  • Type Parameters:
    TData - Type of features in the data set.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvDatasetLoader

    public DatasetLoader<TData>
extends ComponentLoader<TComponent>

    An extended interface ComponentLoader that loads a class Dataset.

    The source of the data set is controllable by any implementor, all that is required is that the raw data is gathered into a class Dataset instance, while satisfying the type constraint TData for individual features in the data set.

    See Also:
    interface ComponentLoader, class Dataset, class Dataset, class Dataset
